' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' NOTES
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

note as n1
  INTERFACE DESIGN RATIONALE
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  ISP (IpcGateway split into domain interfaces):
    ISearchIpc   → search, searchAdvanced, searchSemantic
    ISemanticIpc → getIndexingStatus, cancelIndexing
    ICacheableIpc→ generic invoke / on
    ILogIpc      → writeLog
  IpcGateway implements all four; each consumer
  depends only on the interface it needs (ISP + DIP).

  DIP (Facades & Services behind interfaces):
    Components depend on ISearchFacade,
    ISemanticIndexFacade, IFilterValidator, etc.
    — never on concrete classes directly.
    Enables mock injection in unit tests.

  Strategy Pattern (explicit via interfaces):
    IFilterValueStrategy → Text, Date, Numeric, Enum
      FilterValueInputComponent selects the correct
      strategy at runtime based on FilterFieldType.
    ISubjectDetailStrategy → PF, PG, AS, PAI, PAE, RUP, SW
      SubjectFilterComponent selects the correct
      strategy at runtime based on SubjectType.
      SubjectDetailFormComponent also implements the
      interface as the host form container.

  CONCURRENCY (SearchFacade)
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  isSearching = true  → mutex Signal,
    second submit silently ignored
  AbortController    → cancels in-flight IPC call
  Debounce 300ms     → limits IPC on fast typing

  GRACEFUL DEGRADATION (UC-9.2, UC-11)
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  SemanticIndexFacade.status ≠ 'ready'
    → SearchFacade disables searchSemantic
    → full-text search remains intact
  SemanticIndexStatusComponent shows banner

  USE CASES COVERED
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  UC-9    Full-text free search
  UC-9.1  Advanced filters activation
  UC-9.2  Semantic AI search (optional)
  UC-9.3  Search by class name
  UC-9.4  Search by process ID
  UC-10   Filter pre-validation
  UC-11   Semantic indexing status
  UC-12   Typed filters (Common, DiDai, Aggregate)
  UC-13   Subject filter (3-step wizard)
  UC-15   Results display
  UC-16   No results (EmptyState)
  UC-17   Filter value input
  UC-18   Real-time format validation
end note

